## Concept Nodes

```
id:               habitus
name:             Habitus
originator_id:    bourdieu
date_introduced:  1972
concept_type:     mechanism
abstraction_level: theoretical
status:           active
generation:       3
stream:           identity
notes:            Durable, transposable dispositions acquired through lived experience; operates below conscious awareness
```

```
id:               capital
