originator_id:    bourdieu
date_introduced:  1979
concept_type:     framework
abstraction_level: theoretical
status:           active
generation:       3
stream:           identity
notes:            What you are worth in the field; economic, cultural, social, symbolic; transformation threatens capital devaluation
```

```
id:               hysteresis
name:             Hysteresis
originator_id:    bourdieu
date_introduced:  1977
concept_type:     mechanism
abstraction_level: theoretical
status:           active
generation:       3
stream:           identity
notes:            The lag between a changed field and an unchanged habitus; the mechanism of resistance; entirely rational
```

```
id:               double_bind
